misspecification: C2 test uses CC={10,11,12,17} but C588 suffix-free finding used CC={10,11,12}
explanation: C2 is misspecified like B4. The test expects CC >= 99% suffix-free, but uses CC={10,11,12,17} which includes class 17 (59% suffixed). C588/C590 defined CC suffix-free using CC={10,11,12} (100% suffix-free). M2 reproduces the real C2 rate exactly (both are ~0.834). Correcting C2 pushes M2 from 13/15 to 14/15 = 93.3%. Only B5 remains.
